lead_paragraph: Spain defender Sergio Ramos was surprised to learn that the country's record appearance maker and long-time captain Iker Casillas had been left out of the Spain squad by coach Julen Lopetegui.

headline.print_headline: Ramos Surprised by Casillas Exclusion From Spain Squad
headline.main: Ramos Surprised by Casillas Exclusion From Spain Squad
